id/249/Default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Consensus Statement</a>  opposing further use of dispersants in the Gulf. </p><p>Shaw serves on the International Panel on Chemical Pollution, a select group of scientists urging policymakers to improve management of toxic chemicals. She travels throughout the US, Europe and Asia as a speaker on the ocean crisis and chemical pollution.</p>"}],"url":"https://www.ted.com/talks/susan_shaw_the_oil_spill_s_toxic_trade_off","viewed_count":224214,"talks":[{"curator_approved":true,"description":"Break down the oil slick, keep it off the shores: that's grounds for pumping toxic dispersant into the Gulf, say clean-up overseers. Susan Shaw shows evidence it's sparing some beaches only at devastating cost to the health of the deep sea.","downloads":{"id":925,"languages":[{"languageName":"Russian","endonym":"Русский","languageCode":"ru","ianaCode":"ru","isRtl":false},{"languageName":"French","endonym":"Français","languageCode":"fr","ianaCode":"fr","isRtl":false},{"languageName":"English","endonym":"English","languageCode":"en","ianaCode":"en","isRtl":false},{"languageName":"Dutch","endonym":"Nederlands","languageCode":"nl","ianaCode":"nl","isRtl":false},{"languageName":"German","endonym":"Deutsch","languageCode":"de","ianaCode":"de","isRtl":false},{"languageName":"Korean","endonym":"한국어","languageCode":"ko","ianaCode":"ko","isRtl":false},{"languageName":"Italian","endonym":"Italiano","languageCode":"it","ianaCode":"it","isRtl":false},{"languageName":"Chinese, Simplified","endonym":"中文 (简体)","languageCode":"zh-cn","ianaCode":"zh-Hans","isRtl":false},{"languageName":"Arabic","endonym":"العربية","languageCode":"ar","ianaCode":"ar","isRtl":true},{"languageName":"Portuguese, Brazilian","endonym":"Português brasileiro","languageCode":"pt-br","ianaCode":"pt-BR","isRtl":false},{"languageName":"Polish","endonym":"Polski","languageCode":"pl","ianaCode":"pl","isRtl":false},{"languageName":"Bulgarian","endonym":"български","languageCode":"bg","ianaCod